OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining heavy showers will gradually
OL,7,Fease and clear eastwards, leaving a
OL,8,Flargely dry night with occasional
OL,9,Fclear spells. However, the odd light
OL,10,Fshower remains possible, particularly
OL,11,Fin the west. Mild and breezy
OL,12,Fthroughout.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FIncreasingly cloudy, ahead
OL,15,Fof a band of rain sweeping east across
OL,16,Fthe region. Sunny spells and blustery
OL,17,Fshowers in the afternoon, with hail
OL,18,Fand thunder. Showers easing in the
OL,19,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
